original_title: 新春黄金シリーズ 2022年2月11日 宮城・ゼビオアリーナ仙台
overview: February 11 sees night nine of the New Year’s Golden Series, and the first championship action of the tour, as Sendai will see the IWGP Junior Heavyweight Championship defended atop a card that is dominated by junior heavyweight action.
title: NJPW New Year’s Golden Series Night 9
